<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="background: #f1f1f1">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <% include ../parent/static.ejs %>
    <title><%= com.env.seo.title %>帮助中心</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header" ><a class="iconfont" href="/help"><img src="/img/fh1.png" class="fh_img"></a>流程指引</div>

<div class="help_lists">
    <ul class="help_main">
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>注册？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2"  style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>输入正确的手机号码作为铂恒金服的注册账号</p>
                    <p>  填写短信验证码</p>
                    <p>  设置交易密码</p>
                    <p>  若有邀请码填写邀请码。</p>

                </div>
            </div>

        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg"  class="img1">
                <span>实名？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png"  class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2"  style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>实名信息一旦认证完毕，将不可以修改。</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>绑卡？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>我的账户”-“安全中心”-“我的银行卡”页面输入正确的信息进行绑卡。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>充值？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>4个步骤就可以充值成功。</p>
                    <p>   ①进入“我的账户”，点击“充值”；</p>
                    <p>   ②输入充值金额；</p>
                    <p>  ③可以选择快捷充值或者网银充值；</p>
                    <p>  ④付款后，显示成功付款并跳转到铂恒金服页面，显示充值成功。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>投资？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>根据项目类型、项目周期、年化利率选择标的投资。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>回款？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>投资到期后，本金和利息将回款到您的账户中心，届时也有回款短信通知，您可以选择继续投资。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li>
            <div class="list1">
                <img src="/img/l_03.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <span>提现？</span>
                <img src="/img/12.png" alt="" class="img2">
            </div>
            <div class="list2" style="display: none">
                <img src="/img/m_10.jpg" alt="" class="img1">
                <div class="list2_one">
                    <p>在电脑上：①登录账户，进入“我的账户”，点击“提现”；</p>
                    <p>   ②输入可提现金额；</p>
                    <p>   ③显示提现成功，预计1-2个工作日到账。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </li>
       
    </ul>
</div>
<% include ../parent/slide_nav.ejs %>
</body>
</html>